title: VILLAGE / JOYCE barks
description:
Joyce barks for when she's in the village.

I dared not to move it to her actual folder, cause it's already been inputted and I didn't wanna fuck it up.

dialogueTree.title: Joyce Messier: ""The board is not gonna like it.""
dialogueTree.english: "The board is not gonna like it."

dialogueTree.title: Joyce Messier: ""This place hasn't changed at all.""
Joyce Messier: ""God, I was so young... and stupid.""
dialogueTree.english: "God, I was so young... and stupid."
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Божа, я была такая маладая... і дурная".

dialogueTree.title: Joyce Messier: ""To think I even used to go dancing..."
dialogueTree.english: "To think I even used to go dancing here."
dialogueTree.polish: „I pomyśleć, że nawet przychodziłam tu potańczyć”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: "І падумаць, што нават прыходзіла сюды патанчыць".
